    Expenses:Tax    (10%)
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Test Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-15 Test Payee            Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
